long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Description:
Discover email addresses and phone numbers linked to Instagram profiles with InsEmailFinder, a powerful Chrome extension for marketers and businesses. Quickly and easily extract contact information to streamline your marketing efforts and enhance outreach.

How It Works:
Install InsEmailFinder on Chrome.
Visit an Instagram profile.
Click the extension icon.
View the extracted contact details.

For Marketers and Businesses:
Expand your network.
Connect with influencers.
Conduct market research.
